Package: tradedash
Title: Interactive Trading Dashboard for TradingVerse
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("TradingVerse", "Team", , "trading@verse.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive, production-ready Shiny dashboard application that 
    integrates all TradingVerse packages into a unified interface. Features live 
    market monitoring, strategy development, backtesting, performance analytics,
    and real-time visualization. Designed for quantitative traders and portfolio
    managers who need professional-grade tooling.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
